Completed Fortunes of Umbar Baharbêl daily quests ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Your aid is requested in the continued efforts to improve the fortunes of Umbar Baharbêl.
The Fortunes of Umbar Baharbêl daily quests are available at the Hunter's Expedition Camp, in Rakhatâb, and in Jax Phanâl.
'We must continue to improve the fortunes of Umbar Baharbêl for all of its citizens!\n\n'If you are willing to lend your efforts several more times, I will be able to reward your accomplishments.'
